HEADWORD: Franking
<hw>Frank"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Carp.)</fld> <def>A
method of forming a joint at the intersection of window-sash bars, by
cutting away only enough wood to show a miter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frankish</ent>⟦br⟧
